*Final Table counting all matches:
*                         PP   G   W   D   L  GF  GA  GD
* 1. Botafogo              6  11   7   2   2  31  17  14   champions
* 2. Andarahy              7  12   7   3   2  32  18  14
* 3. Olaria                9  11   6   1   4  23  18   5
